  {
    "title": "Send Help",
    "year": 2026,
    "type": "Movie",
    "poster": "send-help.jpg",
    "rating": "⭐⭐⭐⭐",
    "review": "knew nothing about the film other than raimi directed it, was not disappointed whatsoever. i really love an unreliable narrator story, and i was fully on linda's side because every billionaire should be abolished, and the slow turn and build up of her doing stuff more and more unredeemable was class. i did not see the end coming of her actually having a place, which caught me off guard and made me realize the whole time what i was watching wasn't the story that actually happened. made me want to rewatch immediately to see parts i missed. very fun film \n\nLast Watched: May 17th, 2026",
